{"tid":238205,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[暴雪]2000萬入場費.歐美《鬥陣特攻》職業戰隊相繼退出","createTime":"2017-05-11T01:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T04:10:46.000Z","uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd397c1a14dc0b1b5e0fa0d998a4a206cd7f48a","tid":238205,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32068/overwatch-league-slots-up-to-20-million-and-four-pro-gaming-teams-drop-out\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F32068%2Foverwatch-league-slots-up-to-20-million-and-four-pro-gaming-teams-drop-out&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f65ffc4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/32068/overwatch-league-slots-up-to-20-million-and-four-pro-gaming-teams-drop-out</a><br />\n根據外電 Dot Esports 消息指出，於 2017 年 5 月 9 日美國美式橄欖球聯盟（NFL）的新英格蘭愛國者（New England Patriots ）以及邁阿密海豚（Miami Dolphins）兩支球隊，已向 Blizzard 購買聯賽參賽權，據悉新英格蘭愛國者的交易金額高達 2,000 萬美金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azs51kc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fazs51kc.jpg&h=c94d2558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而，此消息一出，似乎也讓人注意到短短一週內，北美地區有四支電競隊伍相繼退出聯賽，包含知名電競戰隊 Team SoloMid（TSM）、compLexity Gaming、Splyce、以及 Denial eSports 。<br />\n <br />\n首先是 5 月 2 日，Denial Esports 的選手在自己的推特說戰隊解散，海外相關報導也指出隊員們已轉往 Yikes 戰隊。<br />\n<br />\n再來是 TSM 的 b1am 選手在 5 號於推特留言表示，最近他們才剛選完 6 名選手準備預定參加北美聯賽，但經過瞭解 OWL 聯賽的參加金額後（注意留言裡的 $$$ 符號），便決定打退堂鼓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6i1L047.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6i1L047.png&h=35a9dbb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緊接著是 compLexity Gaming 在兩天前（8）於官網發表退出聯賽聲明，表示為選手的將來以及未來電競聯賽的高度，將會為旗下選手積極尋找隊伍。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1W1qy5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1W1qy5U.png&h=a91f0918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣的，北美 Splyce 戰隊的執行長 Marty Strenczewilk 稍早不久也透過影片發布釋出旗下所有選手，退出北美《鬥陣特攻》職業聯賽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX9chE2bbuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrX9chE2bbuQ&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=37871c3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rX9chE2bbuQ</a><br />\n不只是北美地區，就連歐洲賽區的 Red Reserve 也在 5 號發表退出聯賽聲明，但在內容則強調《鬥陣特攻》的努力目前看不到成長，且在歐洲電競市場來說《CS:GO》、《決勝時刻》以及《FIFA》較受歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5999Y4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5999Y4.png&h=cd8e4586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n自從去年推出《鬥陣特攻》獲得成功以來，Blizzard 為推廣屬地制《鬥陣特攻》職業電競聯賽（Overwatch League），積極在海內外號召企業組織參與聯賽，企圖將電競運動升格有如 MLB、NBA 等規模的職業賽事。<br />\n如今有 NFL 這類傳統運動聯盟的球隊加入聯賽，其雄厚的資本市場對 Blizzard 發展電競無疑是件好消息，但對於短缺資金的原生電競隊伍來說恐怕只得忍痛退讓，讓選手到大市場運動組織底下發揮。"},{"pid":"a78c63917ddc3bada101bf4044800d2c3318cc58","tid":238205,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:30:58.000Z","msg":"有2000萬仲駛玩你個聯場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadedb61f1a5a3cd4034d8717370a832365fe8fe","tid":238205,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有2000萬仲駛玩你個聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"73cd297b4b4809396458f75d184695687bd8f423","tid":238205,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有2000萬仲駛玩你個聯場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"4e2c294b9d9c1e3caf571cec8ef4a1e76b9b6ac8","tid":238205,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:04:00.000Z","msg":"食撚懵咗"},{"pid":"6fd4aa862b0f4c6b6dce7bd7857b07d322a1477f","tid":238205,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食撚懵咗</blockquote><br />\n變左有錢佬遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一堆由gaming發育既team跟本參加唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c311ef634d68abaffa24750859e6099fb32bc312","tid":238205,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a29b2c20514a48ad2f44cdd99197c964c8bd3e","tid":238205,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"一個遊戲由盛轉衰既轉捩點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c501e8da82f14ac660f85271770224e1953a1a18","tid":238205,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"開壞個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪個20M <br />\n最後個聯賽搞唔成真係抵撚死"}]}